	<h1 class="title">当中国一片火热时，美国科技公司上市节奏变慢了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99037/small/99037.jpg?1428742661" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">钟舒婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-15 08:59:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10770/medium/10770.jpg?1436645769" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="10770" data-title="《当中国一片火热时，美国科技公司上市节奏变慢了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/10770/medium/10770.jpg?1436645769" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/10770.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
